'''胡戈·耶格'''（{{lang|de|'''Hugo Jaeger'''}}，{{bd|1900年|1月18日|1970年|1月1日}}），德國攝影師，曾擔任納粹德國元首[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]的私人攝影師直到[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]結束。這期間他拍攝了約2000張與希特勒相關的彩色照片，是當時為數不多的[[彩色攝影|彩色攝影]]師<ref name="Hitler up close -- and in color">{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.usatoday.com/ondeadline/2009/06/hitler-up-close-and-in-color.html|title=Hitler up close -- and in color|date=2009-06-04|accessdate=2009-06-06|publisher=''[[今日美國|USA Today]]''|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607103928/http://blogs.usatoday.com/ondeadline/2009/06/hitler-up-close-and-in-color.html|archivedate=2009-06-07}}</ref>。

==經歷==
耶格自1936年起擔任希特勒的私人攝影師，直到1945年第二次世界大戰結束為止<ref name="Unseen photographs reveal the private life of Adolf Hitler">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/5452458/Unseen-photographs-reveal-the-private-life-of-Adolf-Hitler.html|title=Unseen photographs reveal the private life of Adolf Hitler|date=2009-06-05|accessdate=2009-06-06|publisher=''[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]]''|archive-date=2015-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514005545/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/5452458/Unseen-photographs-reveal-the-private-life-of-Adolf-Hitler.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。和另一位希特勒的私人攝影師{{link-en|海因里希·霍夫曼 (攝影師)|Heinrich Hoffmann (photographer)|海因里希·霍夫曼}}不同的是，耶格專門以彩色攝影方式拍攝{{link-en|納粹宣傳|Nazi propaganda}}相關照片<ref>{{Cite news| title = PICTURES OF WORLD WAR II: Hitler in Color | url = http://www.spiegel.de/international/0,1518,339540,00.html | date = 2005-01-31 | publisher = SPIEGEL ONLINE | accessdate = 2009-06-06 }}</ref>。當1945年戰爭即將結束時，耶格將他所拍攝的照片藏入一個行李箱中<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。隨後他碰到美軍士兵時，因為他持有大量納粹相關照片而險些被逮捕<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>，當美軍士兵打開他的箱子時卻被箱內的一瓶[[干邑白蘭地|干邑白蘭地]]所吸引，耶格與美軍士兵共飲該瓶酒而未遭逮捕<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。

之後耶格將他拍攝的照片放在12個玻璃瓶內後埋藏在[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]郊外<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。數年後耶格回到埋藏地點確認當地是安全的<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。1955年耶格挖出照片並送入銀行保險櫃保存<ref name="Hitler up close -- and in color"/><ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>，之後在1965年將照片售予美國《[[生活_(雜誌)|生活]]》雜誌<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。

==死亡與身後==
耶格逝世於1970年1月1日。

生活雜誌網站於2009年6月，[[诺曼底战役|D日]] 65周年時公開了耶格拍攝的照片<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/us_world/2009/06/04/2009-06-04_neverbefore_seen_photos_of_adolf_hitler_taken_by_personal_photographer_revealed.html|title=Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed|date=2009-06-05|accessdate=2009-06-06|publisher=''[[紐約每日新聞|Daily News]]''|archive-date=2009-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822065926/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/us_world/2009/06/04/2009-06-04_neverbefore_seen_photos_of_adolf_hitler_taken_by_personal_photographer_revealed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該網站將耶格的照片公布於4個網路相簿<ref name="Never-before-seen photos of Adolf Hitler taken by personal photographer Hugo Jaeger revealed"/>。其中一張照片是1938年9月1日，希特勒在{{link-en|以阿道夫·希特勒命名的街道列表|List of streets named after Adolf Hitler|阿道夫·希特勒廣場}}向德軍行禮的照片<ref name="Unseen photographs reveal the private life of Adolf Hitler"/>。另一張則是1941年納粹黨領袖群參加聖誕派對照片<ref name="New pictures of Adolf Hitler are released"/>。此外還有1939年希特勒在[[柏林|柏林]]國際汽車展和在一艘郵輪上的照片<ref name="New pictures of Adolf Hitler are released">{{Cite web|url=http://www.wgntv.com/news/wgntv-new-adolph-hitler-photos-published-june5,0,6797835.story|title=New pictures of Adolf Hitler are released|date=2009-06-05|accessdate=2009-06-06|publisher=[[WGN-TV|WGN-TV]].com}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>。

